        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Fixed by not dismissing when `:` comes from a mapping during the expanded cmdline:\n```diff\ndiff --git a/runtime/lua/vim/_core/ui2/messages.lua b/runtime/lua/vim/_core/ui2/messages.lua\nindex 68ae006632..9cc3dbb78f 100644\n--- a/runtime/lua/vim/_core/ui2/messages.lua\n+++ b/runtime/lua/vim/_core/ui2/messages.lua\n@@ -523,7 +523,7 @@ local cmd_on_key = function(key, typed)\n     return\n   end\n   vim.on_key(nil, ui.ns)\n-  if typed == ':' then\n+  if typed == ':' or key == ':' then\n     return -- Keep expanded messages open until cmdline closes.\n   end\n```",
            "created_at": "2026-04-19T15:14:33Z",
